Trophée_Chopard http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Trophée_Chopard 0 Trophée Chopard (English: "Chopard Trophy") is awarded by a jury of professionals to two young actors in order to recognise and encourage their career. It was founded in 2001 by Chopard and has since been presented every year during the Cannes Film Festival.
